/*--set up a git commit base !! managed by heroku!! */
1) git init
2) git add .
3) git commit "initial commit"

/*--deploy to heroku**---
 1) heroku login
 2) heroku create
 3) git remote add heroku
 4) git push heroku master

making some changes to the project--*

 1) git add .
 2) git commit -m "some message"
 3) git push heroku master

